    "longBusinessSummary": "Siam Brothers Vietnam Joint Stock Company produces and trades ropes and fishing nets in Vietnam. The company offers cables covering, eyelet, lead core, aquaculture, onshore fishing net, aquaman, polyester, escape, polypropylene, polyethylene, sailing, safety, and household ropes, as well as strands, twines, nets, PE twines, and rescue rope ladders. It also provides melon hanging, capsicum hanging, anti-falling, green house, hay baler, and banana twines, as well as trellis support ropes. In addition, the company offers floating trash booms, HDPE BUOY, multigrade engine oil, water pumps, plastic trays, ballast, bulbs, lamps, and trawling nets. Further, it produces and sells solar power; produces braids and nets; wholesales synthetics; develops computer software; produces plastic accessories, tools, and equipment; transmits and distributes electricity; and engages in trading of real estate, land use rights of owners, users, or tenants. The company provides its products under Siam Brothers Vietnam, Seahorse, Golden Cock, Cock, Fish & Shrimp, Yet Kieu, Fire Emergency Escape Rope, Siam Eco Farm, PTT Lubricant, and Gata brand names. It serves fishing, maritime transportation, construction, industrial, and agricultural sectors. Siam Brothers Vietnam Joint Stock Company was founded in 1995 and is headquartered in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.",
